      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.Q2xyE1ba2vCOMJt6]{Transmutation}</p>\n<p>Your increased molecular density is disastrous for the weapons of your enemies. While your @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.58zPVi7ejjc6ggof]{Body Array (Ex)} is active, whenever you are struck with a melee weapon, the weapon takes damage equal to your Constitution modifier plus your @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.classes.Item.MMyeA7kL5Vhcio05]{Nanocyte} level. Apply the weaponâ€™s hardness normally. Weapons that take any amount of damage in excess of their hardness gain the broken condition. If the weapon is a natural weapon, the damage is dealt directly to the creature instead; this damage counts as being of any special material if that would bypass any DR that creature has.</p>"
